{"tha-ap316:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap316:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap316:0.3":"Sattapadumiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap316:1.1":"“Nadikule vasamaham, ","tha-ap316:1.2":"nesado nama brahmano; ","tha-ap316:1.3":"Satapattehi pupphehi, ","tha-ap316:1.4":"sammajjitvana assamam. ","tha-ap316:2.1":"Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap316:2.2":"Siddhattham lokanayakam; ","tha-ap316:2.3":"Disva nabhena gacchantam, ","tha-ap316:2.4":"Haso me udapajjatha. ","tha-ap316:3.1":"Paccuggantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap316:3.2":"lokajettham narasabham; ","tha-ap316:3.3":"Assamam atinametva, ","tha-ap316:3.4":"jalajaggehi okirim. ","tha-ap316:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap316:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap316:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap316:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap316:5.1":"Ito te sattame kappe, ","tha-ap316:5.2":"caturo padapavara; ","tha-ap316:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap316:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap316:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap316:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap316:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap316:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sattapadumiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap316:8.1":"Sattapadumiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}